---
---

<section id="statesmans-experience" class="relative py-24 sm:py-32 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Black background with subtle gradient -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#0a0a0a] via-[#0d0d0d] to-[#0a0a0a]"></div>
  <!-- Subtle gold top border -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#c5a44e]/40 to-transparent"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#c5a44e]/40 to-transparent"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <p class="text-[#c5a44e] font-medium tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-xs mb-4">The Pinnacle Experience</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4 font-heading">The Statesman's Experience</h2>
      <div class="w-16 h-px bg-[#c5a44e]/60 mx-auto mb-4"></div>
      <p class="text-white/40 text-lg italic font-heading">An evening within the evening</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Two column: text + image -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center mb-16">
      <!-- Text side -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <p class="text-white/70 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          While thousands celebrate in the grand ballrooms below, a select few will experience the evening from an entirely different vantage point.
        </p>
        <p class="text-white/70 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          The Statesman's Experience begins with a private entrance and a dedicated Ambassador who greets you by name. You'll be escorted to reserved seating on the Presidential Balcony — the same area where dignitaries, honored guests, and All-American Heroes will be celebrated throughout the evening.
        </p>
        <p class="text-white/70 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Between ceremonies and performances, explore exclusive spaces that have hosted presidents and world leaders for over six decades. Enjoy private top-shelf bars, a premium dinner, and backstage access that puts you at the center of the celebration — not just in the audience.
        </p>
        <p class="text-white/70 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Your presence will be celebrated with personal stage announcements and forever memorialized in the official event program — a lasting record of those who were in the room when history was made.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Image side -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-2xl aspect-[4/3]">
          <img
            src="/images/event/statesman-vip-dinner.png"
            alt="An intimate VIP dinner — candelabras, champagne, and distinguished guests"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <!-- Subtle gold corner accents -->
        <div class="absolute -top-3 -left-3 w-12 h-12 border-t border-l border-[#c5a44e]/30"></div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-3 -right-3 w-12 h-12 border-b border-r border-[#c5a44e]/30"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Centered closing line -->
    <p class="text-center text-[#c5a44e]/80 text-lg font-medium font-heading italic mb-16">
      This is not a ticket upgrade. It is a fundamentally different evening.
    </p>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="text-center">
      <button
        class="eventbrite-checkout inline-block border border-[#c5a44e]/60 text-[#c5a44e] px-12 py-4 text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase hover:bg-[#c5a44e]/10 transition-all rounded cursor-pointer"
      >
        Reserve Your Place
      </button>
      <p class="text-white/25 text-xs tracking-wider uppercase mt-4">Very limited availability</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
